{"tid":508532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【飛雞】印尼crew話酒店泳池細過佢屋企果個","createTime":"2017-12-24T10:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T20:10:36.000Z","uid":161438,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"419be5652ece58e73bdbeafbefd2571e77347b62","tid":508532,"uid":161438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"話說早排同個印尼gay crew飛雅加達<br />\n然後我話我一陣想去泳池游水<br />\n佢輕描淡寫咁講：「個泳池細過我屋企果個。」<br />\nMe： <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢繼續話：我們好多都係唔洗做都得，只係我地護照去好多地方要visa，做crew就可以周圍去又唔洗visa... 係呢，你哋要俾家用架嘛，我地唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMe：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來我份工對佢地黎講係生活態度，我而我黎講係無咁痛苦嘅生存之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba7b3dfc29a2cee156064ee3b1edc81d9d3a6dc","tid":508532,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"有錢唔做美加人？去邊都得"},{"pid":"50899653615fb8692de00a80515743789b9a74ee","tid":508532,"uid":158180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:49:41.000Z","msg":"有錢怕咩做visa?<br />\n畀錢人搞都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dce8f7491b323201670c1dc84a5c87ec90d2a0f","tid":508532,"uid":161438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T20:10:36.000Z","msg":"佢地嘅有錢應該係相對當地嘅窮人<br />\n我估佢地起豪宅連泳池都係等於我地嘅首期<br />\n同樣嘅人工 我係香港買唔到樓 佢夠洗夠用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}